From c2c62e8ba8fba77cd4f53eefc2d57194b578e9a6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Manner <daniel.manner@equinox-solutions.de>
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 2026 19:46:14 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] DESS: Fix SolarThrottlingIssue on MultiRS Devices.

Updated Calculations to use AcPowerSetpoint
Updated Idling to use AcPowerSetpoint as well (RS)
Removed trailing whitespaces (automatic from now on)
Fixed unittests
If no external mppt power present, use Disable-Features of the RS.
---
 delegates/dynamicess.py  | 258 ++++++++++++--------
 tests/dynamicess_test.py | 513 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 2 files changed, 608 insertions(+), 163 deletions(-)

